' *** SM_X100.LST ***                                2nd GFA-Manual, page 16-12
> PROCEDURE sm_start_x100
  '
  ' *** Start Soundmachine-song (if necessary, unpack first)
  ' *** Use in X100-mode only
  ' *** After @sm_space(TRUE) a <Space> will stop the song
  '
  ' *** Procedure:  Sm_space  Sm_wait
  ' *** Standard:  on!  off!
  '
  @sm_space(on!)
  SPOKE &HFFFA19,1
  @sm_wait
  @sm_space(off!)
RETURN
' *********
'
